---
import Layout from "~/layouts/Layout.astro";
import Section from "~/components/Section.astro";
import Container from "~/components/Container.astro";
import Heading from "~/components/Heading.astro";
---

<Layout pageTitle="About Us" title="About Us">
	<Section class:list={"bg-gray-50"}>
		<Container>
			<Heading>
				<h1 slot="heading-title">About Us</h1>
				<p slot="heading-content">
					Car Key Supply LLC is proud to give used OEM car keys a second life. We buy unwanted keys from
					drivers, locksmiths, and vendors, then professionally refurbish them so they can be reused by us or
					by locksmiths across the country.
				</p>
			</Heading>
		</Container>
	</Section>

	<Section>
		<Container>
			<Heading>
				<h2 slot="heading-title">Our Mission</h2>
				<p slot="heading-content">
					Our mission is simple: make it easy to sell used and unwanted car keys while keeping more reusable
					OEM keys in circulation. We focus on competitive pricing, honest communication, and fast payment so
					our vendors always know they are working with a company they can trust.
				</p>
			</Heading>
		</Container>
	</Section>

	<Section class:list={"bg-gray-50"}>
		<Container>
			<Heading>
				<h2 slot="heading-title">Why Vendors Work With Us</h2>
				<p slot="heading-content">
					With nearly 10 years of experience, we understand the value of used car keys and the importance of
					reliable service. Based in Central New York, we are a professional refurbisher of used car keys and
					also provide locksmith services throughout the region. We work hard to build long-term relationships
					by staying responsive, paying quickly, and treating every transaction with professionalism.
				</p>
			</Heading>
		</Container>
	</Section>
</Layout>
